{"tid":2441333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★兩童疑遭親父繼母虐待---打至流血結焦 捏傷口、連屎都食，拿著膠兜在門口食......","createTime":"2021-03-10T15:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T18:21:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"edb6a8a46fc8277734a268614ce8767c47be4a77","tid":2441333,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"小兄妹疑遭親父和繼母虐待5個月，5歲妹妹更喪命案續審，繼母與前夫所生的女兒Y作供，庭上播放Y的會面錄影，Y透露出她與這對沒有血緣關係的兄妹在家中有著不同的待遇，她指小兄妹被父母用拖鞋和藤條打，更被打至流血結焦，而她則沒有被打。她又指小兄妹不會與她和父母等人同枱食飯，只拿著膠兜在門口食。她又指小兄妹欠自理能力，會捏傷口，Y並說：「可能佢地想傷口爛掛，佢地<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>連屎都食</strong></span>。」她又稱，妹妹去世前曾稱「暈暈地」及「好驚」，之後昏倒過去。<br />\n<br />\n控方庭上播放Y的錄影會面，講述與父母(男及女被告)、婆婆(第三被告，即女被告的母親)、哥哥(男童X)和妹妹(女童Z)同住的情況。女童Z於2018年1月6日被證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n母曾著要拋高妹妹Z令她知驚<br />\n<br />\nY在案發時7歲，她稱於2018年1月5日晚餐前，爸爸和妹妹玩「飛高高」的拋高遊戲。媽媽著爸爸要拋高妹妹，令她的頭撞天花板。被問及為何要玩至撞到天光板，Y指因「用膝條打佢(Z)都無效，想佢知驚」。<br />\n<br />\n妹妹叫唔好爸爸露不悅表情<br />\n<br />\nY指，爸爸跟妹妹玩了「飛高高」11次，其中7、8次撞到天花板，撞到天花板時都「好大聲」，當時妹妹叫「唔好」，而父親的表情則「嬲嬲地」。Y和哥哥當晚也有玩「飛高高」，但她的頭未有撞到天花板，而她玩得很開心。<br />\n<br />\n之後，父母再跟妹妹玩「扮超人」三四次，「一人一邊」捉著妹妹的手腳，再搖動她。而妹妹當時感驚慌，亦叫「唔好」。Y又補充，哥哥當時因做錯事，需站在門口。<br />\n<br />\n小兄妹未與父母同枱食飯<br />\n<br />\n因妹妹行路時「賴皮」，坐在地下不動，所以Y和父母吃飯時，妹妹需「行一條線」。而哥哥和妹妹之後在門口用膳，「攞住膠兜食」。Y解釋，因父母和婆婆都指，哥哥和妹妹沒有餐桌禮儀，所以哥哥和妹妹不能一同進食。<br />\n<br />\n哥哥和妹妹當晚則在客廳的角落，在睡袋入睡。至翌日早上，妹妹「暈暈地」，又稱「我好驚」，最終暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n小兄妹被打50次 隔日便打<br />\n<br />\nY又指，哥哥和妹妹之前因為頑皮，「三分顏色上大紅」，遭父母用藤條和拖鞋打。父母會用拖鞋打至對方的嘴流血，拖鞋亦留有血跡。此外，爸爸亦有揮拳。她補充，哥哥和妹妹亦於1月5日早上，因做錯事而被打。<br />\n<br />\n她透露哥哥和妹妹各被打50次，隔日便被打。而婆婆亦覺得哥哥和妹妹頑皮，有用藤條打哥哥。Y透露，自己未有被打。<br />\n<br />\n見小兄妹連屎都食<br />\n<br />\nY亦指哥哥和妹妹的自理能力較差，會捏自己的傷口，並說：「可能佢地想傷口爛掛，佢地連屎都食。」Y又稱聽到父母對話間提過，因不想讓老師見到哥哥的傷口，因此不讓他上學。而妹妹則因跟不上老師的教學進度，因此未有返學。<br />\n<br />\n小兄妹污糟邋遢要瞓睡袋<br />\n<br />\nY在錄影會面又指，哥哥和妹妹有時因「污糟邋遢」，而不可在床上入睡。Y指兩人在睡袋入睡共15至20次。<br />\n<br />\nY又指，雖然哥哥被打至傷口結焦，但未有看醫生。若情況嚴重，父母會替他消毒和搽藥膏。<br />\n<br />\n指飛高高是逗家中小朋友的遊戲<br />\n<br />\n而辯方盤問時問Y，Y在錄影會面中提及「佢地連屎都食」是否真的有發生，Y回應指不記得。辯方又問，妹妹是否曾玩自己的糞便，並用糞便弄髒Y的床，Y同樣稱不記得。但Y同意「飛高高」是遊戲，逗家中的小朋友開心。<br />\n<br />\n而婆婆的律師指，婆婆沒有用藤條打哥哥和妹妹，Y不同意。<br />\n<br />\n三名被告：<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>男被告（29歲，運輪工人)</strong></span>，為涉案男童X和女童Z的親父；女被告（30歲，家庭主婦)，為男被告的第二任妻子，亦即X和Z的繼母；第三被告(56歲，會計文員)，是女被告的母親。男及女被告被控1項謀殺罪，指他們於2018年1月6日謀殺Z。此外，第三被告則否認4項殘酷對待兒童罪，控罪指她於2017年8月10日至2018年1月6日，故意虐待和忽略X和Z。X和Z在案發時分別8和5歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/597419/%E5%85%A9%E7%AB%A5%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E8%A6%AA%E7%88%B6%E7%B9%BC%E6%AF%8D%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E6%A1%88-%E7%B9%BC%E6%AF%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E4%BA%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%BE%85%E9%81%87-%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%84%E5%A6%B9%E9%80%A3%E5%B1%8E%E9%83%BD%E9%A3%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F597419%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%2588%25B6%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%2599%2590%25E5%25BE%2585%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BE%2585%25E9%2581%2587-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2585%2584%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%25B1%258E%25E9%2583%25BD%25E9%25A3%259F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=5c16ea57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/597419/%E5%85%A9%E7%AB%A5%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E8%A6%AA%E7%88%B6%E7%B9%BC%E6%AF%8D%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E6%A1%88-%E7%B9%BC%E6%AF%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E4%BA%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%BE%85%E9%81%87-%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%8F%E5%85%84%E5%A6%B9%E9%80%A3%E5%B1%8E%E9%83%BD%E9%A3%9F</a>"},{"pid":"3d64749ffd1c2f737ca5df44929b0730b3bd7bbb","tid":2441333,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"Lihkg話 &ldquo;生仔抗支&rdquo;撚呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35248f53717013a8436431905b9d00bf46e2bd74","tid":2441333,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"Lihkg生仔撚：特訓來的，將來抗支用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ba03e19428b44a6e572c2ee46fbd4bd2a78233","tid":2441333,"uid":162954,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 佢入冊實俾人打撚到仆街"},{"pid":"6dd76313c4da803c3614deb9ba148d2ed47464d1","tid":2441333,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:19:01.000Z","msg":"會捏傷口，Y並說：「<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>可能佢地想傷口爛掛，</strong></span>佢地連屎都食。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b810961a596c36ff2266613207debe8a57bb8bf","tid":2441333,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"父母用藤條和拖鞋打。父母會用拖鞋打至對方的嘴流血，拖鞋亦留有血跡。此外，爸爸亦有揮拳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40abe27906eb21372f4ae151dd80c68ef870335","tid":2441333,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"hellokitty人頭案咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在傷口上塗上辣椒油，逼吞吃糞便及喝尿[8][9]。被告之後把燒熔的塑膠吸管滴在她的腿上，並命令受害人發出笑聲。受害人開始神志不清，並不時挑起傷口上的焦疤"},{"pid":"d202fedf3e3d8465a7f2999d5870c54b49a0e74b","tid":2441333,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd4015252a7b232366696f035d986810b5f2e7b","tid":2441333,"uid":358968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"而婆婆的律師指，婆婆沒有用藤條打哥哥和妹妹，Y不同意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n踢爆婆婆,Y 妹妹會唔會都俾人出氣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf41269595941fd706c9f88507830fc165b5b26","tid":2441333,"uid":192573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"個繼母真係賤女人 好撚惡毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個老豆真係垃圾屎 好撚冷血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfe02dd8d06d6a03451e59438dab67ee170533f","tid":2441333,"uid":77707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"善惡頭來終有報"},{"pid":"2173889b59a4ce2196e578d54f0a78f8a8f0ab82","tid":2441333,"uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zoRAUqYG2Is&amp;t=3s&amp;ab_channel=SnakeWan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzoRAUqYG2Is%26t%3D3s%26ab_channel%3DSnakeWan&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=25b04b3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zoRAUqYG2Is&amp;t=3s&amp;ab_channel=SnakeWan</a>"},{"pid":"4c593c45614d8f88867d271ef3b9b8defd532a5f","tid":2441333,"uid":141681,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"咩叫唔記得有冇食屎，唔記得嘅嘢一開始做咩講出嚟? 係咪爆響口之後想隱瞞，定係想鬧人食屎? 睇嚟呢隻小傻閪遺傳哂佢老母啲犯賤"},{"pid":"eefcf0bd90f1b524b605988e3ede439e2f0cc812","tid":2441333,"uid":9412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4cd4015252a7b232366696f035d986810b5f2e7b","tid":2441333,"uid":358968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"而婆婆的律師指，婆婆沒有用藤條打哥哥和妹妹，Y不同意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n踢爆婆婆,Y 妹妹會唔會都俾人出氣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"正常都唔會仲一齊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fdd824e2925f0b4dd9b22ded54c0cbbf2d7542","tid":2441333,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"愈睇愈火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692022acdf8b1e2dd53bd98982a1744d4d7026f2","tid":2441333,"uid":178882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace662e23db2ee34c79594680667ad4e9147f41d","tid":2441333,"uid":59242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"fb33819abbc8f432e83550ca2260060e2d291515","tid":2441333,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"異性戀又贏"}]}